[bullet] Chemical Name:  |  Dosage: 

The prescribed individual is allowed to possess at most 200u of each chemical at a given moment. The recommended form of prescribed chemicals is in pill form, with both the pills and bottles properly labelled, however injection needles and a jug can be used at the discretion of the Chief Medical Officer. The prescribed individual is not allowed to distribute their prescribed medicines to other individuals.

